    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute perfection for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable, clean, and drives like a dream! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. It's ready for its next adventure, whether that's your daily commute or a fun weekend road trip. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
