    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This specimen is equipped with the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. The mechanical integrity is excellent, with a documented VANOS overhaul, valve clearance adjustment, and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains exceptionally potent, delivering linear torque and that signature metallic rasp through the quad-exit exhaust. A mechanically robust example ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
