    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape! It drives super smooth and has been well-loved, making it perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend road trip. It's ready to hit the road whenever you are\u2014come take it for a spin!",
